---
title: Mixed Mushroom and Truffle Pizza with DIY Bechamel Sauce and Chives
description: Creamy DIY bechamel sauce is a luxurious base for this rich mushroom pizza. Dial up the decadence factor with a sprinkle of truffle salt!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1046_W33_CA_RV161331-1_Mainlow-2224ea00.jpg
